  "title": "Every Power Dominates the Logarithm",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "For every $r > 0$:\n\\[\n \\lim_{x \\to \\infty} \\frac{\\ln x}{x^r} = 0\n \\qquad\\text{and}\\qquad\n \\lim_{x \\to 0^+} x^r \\ln x = 0.\n\\]",
